*bash-3.0-r10 (29 Apr 2005)

  29 Apr 2005; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> +files/bash-3.0-afs.patch,
  +files/bash-3.0-crash.patch, +files/bash-3.0-darwin-conn.patch,
